LICENSE INFORMATION FOR MTProxy PROJECT
=======================================

This project uses multiple licenses depending on the components:

1. APPLICATION COMPONENTS (main proxy server):
   The main MTProxy application is licensed under the GNU General Public License 
   version 2 (GPLv2), with the additional exemption that compiling, linking, 
   and/or using OpenSSL is allowed. You are free to remove this exemption 
   from derived works.

   See the file GPLv2 for the complete license text.

2. LIBRARY COMPONENTS (utility libraries):
   The MTProto-proxy Library components are licensed under the GNU Lesser 
   General Public License version 2.1 (LGPLv2.1).

   See the file LGPLv2 for the complete license text.

