ADDITIONAL NOTES
================

- The project is composed of both application code (licensed under GPL v2) 
  and library code (licensed under LGPL v2.1)
- Both licenses require that the source code be made available when 
  distributing modified versions
- The OpenSSL exemption allows the use of OpenSSL cryptographic libraries 
  without requiring the entire application to be licensed under GPL

For more information about these licenses, visit:
- GPL: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html
- LGPL: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl-2.1.html